# Commands you should run
Run a build via `flutter build` (add platform if needed: `flutter build apk`, `flutter build ios`, `flutter build web`, etc.).
Run tests via `flutter test`.
Install dependencies via `flutter pub get`.
Stage files to git with `git add .`
Commit files to git with `git commit -m 'ADD_DESCRIPTION_HERE'`
Run the app in debug mode with `flutter run` (add device flags if needed).

Default to desktop build for development and testing.